name: The Golden GOAT
description: Celebrating a life.  Betty white was born on January 17,1922. Betty white was the first women to produce a sitcom. She kept a lot of families happy, she's was known to be the sweetest with a sense of humor few could imagine. Betty white even dabbed it once. Today we Celebrate her life and her passing into the other plane. ALL CAPS to a greatest of all time. This is my tribute. H. E. Double hockey sticks..
